OL,3,CFire damages Clarkson's Farm star
OL,4,CKaleb Cooper's barn
OL,6,FClarkson's Farm star Kaleb Cooper's
OL,7,Fbarn in Oxfordshire has been damaged
OL,8,Fby fire.
OL,10,FThe 27-year-old, who has a small
OL,11,Fholding in Chipping Norton, rose to
OL,12,Ffame through his role as Jeremy
OL,13,FClarkson's farm manager.
OL,15,FPosting on his Instagram stories on
OL,16,FWednesday (22 April), he displayed a
OL,17,Fphoto of the damage along with the
OL,18,Fcaption: "I'm having a bad day. Anyone
OL,19,Fgot any straw, lost mine."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
