OL,3,CFire damages Clarkson's Farm star
OL,4,CKaleb Cooper's barn
OL,6,FAlongside his role on Clarkson's Farm,
OL,7,FMr Cooper has previously supported
OL,8,Fstudents wanting to study agriculture
OL,9,Fand also released a charity single
OL,10,Faimed at raising awareness of the
OL,11,Fstruggles faced by farmers.
OL,13,FMr Cooper had already worked on the
OL,14,Ffarm owned by Jeremy Clarkson for
OL,15,Fthree years before he was appointed as
OL,16,Fmanager after Mr Clarkson took on the
OL,17,Frunning of the farm in 2019.
OL,19,FAt the age of 14, Mr Cooper was
OL,20,Falready breeding sheep and working on
OL,21,Fa dairy farm.
